Jelian, Goddess of Whispers
Born from the silence between heartbeats, Jelian emerged as the keeper of secrets that mortals and gods alike feared to speak aloud. Her voice is never heard directly but carried through echoes and murmurs,
guiding those who listen with patience. She thrives in twilight, where hidden truths slip through the veil of shadows.


Amihan(Air)
Amihan, child of the northern wind, was gifted with the freedom to roam the skies and the power to carry life or ruin with a single breath. Gentle in spirit yet bound by duty, she calms the seas for travelers
but can summon storms when balance is threatened. Her presence is the promise of change, ever restless and ever watchful.


Dirk, Guardian of Growth and Harvest
Emerged from the heart of Siera Madre, they said it to be the child of the world's heartbeat. Yet, whispered among the villages was a warning—that such a gift bore the weight of endless sacrifice. Every field of soil flourished, as if they bow when his presences lingers among land. His dedication and vow to provide protection the lands made it his life's value, as much as he values the soil. 
A skillful warrior with a heart made with steel, capable of upbringing his earthly prowess.

Danaya (Earth)
There were tales of a daughter with immense power to ever lay on land. Born from the first stone kissed by sunlight, she embodies endurance and unyielding strength. Her touch can heal barren ground or summon quakes that reshape mountains, for she is both nurturer and destroyer. Steadfast and resolute, Danaya stands as the silent foundation upon which all life endures.

Joygen, The Goddess of Eternal Blaze 
Born from a spark that lit the first star, controls fire to create life or destroy evil. 
She can purify souls with flames, command sunlight to grow crops or burn lands, forge weapons that never break, and help beings rise a new from ashes. But her power fades in darkness, and if misused, her fires rage uncontrollably.

Perina(Fire)
Born when the moon’s shattered core bled into the mortal realm, carries a soul bound to fractured starlight a curse that grants her power to mend broken realms but drains mortal hearts of hope.
She commands flames to incinerate enemies, ignite weapons with scorching power. However, her power diminishes in the presence of strong water magic or when faced with overwhelming grief, as her strength is fueled by passion and will.
